{"tid":2141844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民總辭先係最戇鳩","createTime":"2020-08-06T04:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:04:40.000Z","uid":282438,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"00b90b60b186299abd2f51bcb485b5f3a853dbcf","tid":2141844,"uid":282438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:17:33.000Z","msg":"依家柒婆一定會推遲一年先再選舉<br />\n呢一年所有議員安排係佢個大難題<br />\n俾DQ左既議員繼續坐阿爺唔俾<br />\n佢自己全部委任更加唔得<br />\n點做柒婆都煩，泛民只需要企定定就可以<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個時候走出黎話總辭既<span class=\"red\">一定係鬼，係五毛</span><br />\n明明對家自殺緊仲走出黎俾位柒婆落台既<span class=\"red\">一定係鬼，係五毛</span><br />\n總辭後幻想迫佢重選既<span class=\"red\">一定係鬼，係五毛</span><br />\n<br />\n柒婆推遲得選舉，自然都可以推遲埋重選<br />\n到時仲可以大條道理委任晒全部議席<br />\n所以依家幫對家落台既<span class=\"red\">一定係鬼，係五毛</span><br />\n(很重要所以要講四次)"},{"pid":"f7aba552f99778a4cfb0aafb4cafb0756718bed4","tid":2141844,"uid":282438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"邊3條 就咁放低負評就走左?<br />\n<br />\n識唔識打字，表達吓你負評既高見"},{"pid":"4cca257d4a00e42a772ea74647af3eaad658e1dc","tid":2141844,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:56:50.000Z","msg":"呀Q完未<br />\n<br />\n人地一早傾好晒 <br />\n自殺？ <br />\n<br />\n根本辭左 迫佢重選 <br />\n佢選唔選都死就真"},{"pid":"b1d4f1c3392c9409d732e8bf28e784c6611d92b5","tid":2141844,"uid":53268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"爺你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8228aa67e48b4f6d33c3f21374cf69eb4dff38d0","tid":2141844,"uid":282438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cca257d4a00e42a772ea74647af3eaad658e1dc","tid":2141844,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:56:50.000Z","msg":"呀Q完未<br />\n<br />\n人地一早傾好晒 <br />\n自殺？ <br />\n<br />\n根本辭左 迫佢重選 <br />\n佢選唔選都死就真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"你話我係阿Q<br />\n咁你就係幻想<br />\n<br />\n幻想總辭後會重選<br />\n你夠鐘午睡喇"},{"pid":"9951b39c553f6273e8ac028358bbfe9f445f1ca0","tid":2141844,"uid":275692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"總辭之後會話疫情問題唔適合選舉<br />\n全部空位用委任方法<br />\n不過咁樣仲好 加速主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2affacd59a3b34be822c12656c9d3a1ae1bdd61","tid":2141844,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩先捉左林夕呢隻畀教主圈養既熱狗共諜出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db4a2f0e5c1623e5c240613ad9689b0b9b98bd5","tid":2141844,"uid":317956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"其實做咩都只係向國際表態<br />\n你就算成個議會都係黃又點<br />\n之前立咁多條法那有一條要經垃圾會<br />\n選舉目的根本唔係要贏而係令對方難睇ok？"},{"pid":"86adad146a95152c7e721d4e019b432a233313df","tid":2141844,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"贊成中共處理dq議員係個難題<br />\n<br />\n不過宜家大把野唔經立法會，唔好幻想係入面除咗落港共面會有其他作用<br />\n<br />\nbtw，爺你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"5c5ba675b2e2680556dff4a5b51bed9f3c04991e","tid":2141844,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"林夕係鬼，分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203872ac0cee5420f83d7b9c8e0eae538b3a5f31","tid":2141844,"uid":79993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"其實都係，要總辭係都等政府宣佈左點安排先，到時唔俾你做又可以攞多個pt做外宣，俾你做到時話總辭又得<br />\n<br />\n宜家總辭咪等於林鄭政府多謝你解決左個難題"},{"pid":"a2ebeab6bf152654ec19aca28a3f865df9c8a915","tid":2141844,"uid":358948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"林夕都係鬼？<br />\n泛民打手無恥至極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左出糧乜都敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如你地返大灣區五毛五毛咁出糧啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf44daa7d34c92002b54d7cfd2483dc3ad23a22","tid":2141844,"uid":292739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d4f1c3392c9409d732e8bf28e784c6611d92b5","tid":2141844,"uid":53268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"爺你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04dcdaa13e5159b1d45a2e15026fb7b82cc659c","tid":2141844,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"我反對總辭，原因係<br />\n<br />\n總辭只可以造成一日的頭條。<br />\n<br />\n不總辭的話，泛民的聲音可以全年有全世界記者報導，保皇黨在議會內9up, 泛民可以力斥其非，令其出醜當場。留在議會，可以令到保皇黨出錯的機會大增。不留在議會，只會將發言機會拱手相讓。"}]}